{\fs22\f2 {\cf2\ltrch Blender\rquote s }{\loch\f3\cf2\ltrch interface is }{\cf2\ltrch separated into three main parts:}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\fs22\f2 \li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\fs22\f2 {\cf2\ltrch The Topbar at the very top, consists of the main menu, which is used for saving, importing and exporting files, configuring settings, and rendering among other functions.}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\fs22\f2 \li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\fs22\f2 {\ltrch Areas in the middle, which is the main workspace}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\fs22\f2 \li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\fs22\f2 {\ltrch The Status Bar at the bottom, which displays shortcut suggestions and relevant statistics.}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
